Ubuntu 20.04 have defualt python3 not include python2 so if you type #python command not found only have #python3 so let we setup to found #python command.


Ubuntu 20.04 Python version switch manager
=====================================================

# ls /usr/bin/python*

# sudo update-alternatives --list python

# sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python2 1

# sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python3 2

# sudo update-alternatives --list python    ### Check lists

# sudo update-alternatives --config python

# python -V
